      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "……弱小事務所のくせに、結構いい寮に住んでるのね\nほら、着いたわよ。ちゃんと歩きなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…For a small agency‚ you guys live in a pretty nice dorm\nHey‚ we're here‚ Walk properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.0999999842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.3333334208
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.8000000875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "だいたい、仕事終わりに居酒屋直行するアイドルって\n週刊誌に書かれたらたまったもんじゃないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriousely‚ an idol goes straight to a bar right after work‚\nif it's published in a weekly magazine‚ it's a big news",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5999999842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.7666666509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "らって～、franさんとお仕事一緒で\n超、超超～楽しかったんだもーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But~‚ working with fran-san was\nreally‚ really-really~ funー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7666666509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.9333336991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな機会、めったにないじゃなーい？\nローカルラジオの番組に二人でゲスト出演！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chances like this don't come around oftenー?\nThe two of us appeared as guests on a local radio show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333336991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.6999990941
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "楽しかった～って、30分そこら喋っただけでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say it was fun‚ but we only talked for about 30 minutes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6999990941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.2666657608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "オッケーオッケー！\nオ～～ルオッケ～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "OKー OKー!\nO~~Kay~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2666657608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.866666778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "プロデューサーが二人のファンなだけで呼ぶって……\n職権乱用過ぎ。知り合いだけど、断れば良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The producer contacted us because he's a fan of both of us…\nThat's such an abuse of power‚ I know him‚ but it would be better to refuse",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.866666778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.0333354792
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事でもご飯でもfranさんと一緒とか\nハッピーだわ～！　イェーイ！　ハイタ～ッチ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Working and eating with fran-san\nIt's so happy~! Yay! High touch~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0333354792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.7666662694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子が奢るって言うから一緒にご飯行っただけだし\nこんなにべろべろになれるなんて、ある種才能だわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko offered to treat me‚ so I went to eat together\nBeing able to get so drunk‚ it's some kind of talent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7666662694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.2666662694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "才能～？　えへへ、遙子てんしゃいってことかしら\nイェーイ！　てんしゃいセブンティーーン！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talent~? Ehehe‚ Are you saying Haruko is a genius?\nYay! Genius Sevenーーteen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2666662694,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
