      "text": "はいはい、もうそれでいいわよ\nそれじゃあね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah‚ that's fine\nThen‚ good bye",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7666713557,
      "sfxList": [
