      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_04-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃぁ～、遙子の部屋が二軒目ねぇ～！\nおばあちゃんからもらった、ワインがあるのよぉ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then~‚ the second spot is Haruko's room~!\nI have some wine that I got from my grandma…",
        "id": ""
